  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in the ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the smoked salmon and cook until heated through, about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and lemon juice.",
    "Serve the smoked salmon mixture over cauliflower rice.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley and lemon wedges, if desired."
